      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "047a5b235dc8c6b0",
      "text": "Light gun [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Light_gun wikipedia] is a pointing device for computers and a control device for arcade and video games, typically shaped to resemble a pistol. "
    },
